The German regional state of Saxony-
Anhalt may help  Q-Cells SE (QCE)  in a restructuring effort,
Mitteldeutsche Zeitung  reported , citing an interview with Jens
Bullerjahn, the stateâ€™s finance minister.  The state is open to talks about support if the company can
